Package: openaiapi
Title: R Interface to the OpenAI API
Version: 0.0.1
URL: https://github.com/robonomist/openaiapi, https://robonomist.github.io/openaiapi/
Authors@R:
    person("Juha", "Itkonen", , "juha@robonomist.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: openaiapi is an R package that provides a comprehensive and faithful interface to the OpenAI API. It closely mirrors the API structure while offering R6 classes for convenient handling of API objects.
